    <item>
      <title>交易商等待特朗普就加拿大石油关税做出决定，油价停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普决定对加拿大和墨西哥征收关税，油价回吐早前的涨幅，交易几乎没有变化，但交易员们猜测这是否包括原油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 23:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
